inct in France. Compare   Ballanger   1 and   Bellenger   1."]}]},{"name":"Johannes","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["New Testament: ‘God is gracious’.  See  <b>John</b> ."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["form of   John  , also used quite frequently in the English-speaking world. In Northern Ireland it is sometimes found as a variant of   Ewan ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Johannes Bellingers was born on 28 April 1579, in Stuttgart, Württemberg. He had at least 1 daughter with Mrs Johannes Bellingers. He died in 1640, at the age of 61."},"et":{"28 April 1579–1640":"28. aprill 1579–1640","–Female":"Surnud","1632–Female":"1632–Surnud","1579–1640":"1579–1640","1579":"1579","28 April 1579":"28. aprill 1579","1632":"1632","1640":"1640","22 October 1632":"22. oktoober 1632","Stuttgart, Württemberg":"Stuttgart, Württemberg","Württemberg, Germany":"Württemberg, Saksamaa"},"fi":{"28 April 1579–1640":"28. huhtikuuta 1579–1640","–Female":"Kuollut","1632–Female":"1632–Kuollut","1579–1640":"1579–1640","1579":"1579","28 April 1579":"28. huhtikuuta 1579","1632":"1632","1640":"1640","22 October 1632":"22. lokakuuta 1632","Stuttgart, Württemberg":"Stuttgart, Württemberg","Württemberg, Germany":"Württemberg, Saksa"},"fr":{"28 April 1579–1640":"28 avril 1579–1640","–Female":"Décédée","1632–Female":"1632–Décédée","1579–1640":"1579–1640","1579":"1579","28 April 1579":"28 avril 1579","1632":"1632","1640":"1640","22 October 1632":"22 octobre 1632","Stuttgart, Württemberg":"Stuttgart, Württemberg","Württemberg, Germany":"Württemberg, Allemagne","lifeSummary":"Johannes Bellingers est né le 28 avril 1579, à Stuttgart, Württemberg. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Mrs Johannes Bellingers. Il est décédé en 1640, à l’âge de 61 ans."},"de":{"28 April 1579–1640":"28. April 1579–1640","–Female":"Verstorben","1632–Female":"1632–Verstorben","1579–1640":"1579–1640","1579":"1579","28 April 1579":"28. April 1579","1